Maxima came to. As her optics - which were once clear blue, were now crimson 
red - flashed brightly. She sat up & swung her new legs over the side of the 
table. Then leapt off the table. 

Her sleek new form more metallic than the last one, was nearly as dangerous 
as her old style form. 

She turned to face Perceptor. &quot;You have done well, Perceptor. You are to be 
commended.&quot; Her voice this time was less feline & more like her old original 
voice. There was more of her orginal form to this new appearance than her 
previous techno -organic form. 

Now... at full power & strength.. she was ready for anything. 

Her optics glanced about, then spotted off into the CR the form of Hydras. 
&quot;Status on Hydras,&quot; she asked. 

